enhanced_by.reason: The normalizeTag method is used to normalize the tag name, which is a critical step in the valueOf method.
The lowerCase method is used to normalize the tag name to lowercase, which is a similar transformation step as in the valueOf method.
The isKnownTag method checks if a tag is pre-defined, which is a similar verification step as checking if the tag is already in the Tags map in the valueOf method.
The isBlock method checks if a tag is a block tag, which is a similar verification step as checking the tag's properties in the valueOf method.
